Danny recaps this week's Vanderpump Rules, where the gang has a soft opening for TomTom, an uninvited Kristen eats pasta from bed with her dogs & a camera crew, and Lala plans to take the PJ to Solvang.


#PumpRules Recap-- 9:22ish
